rd time\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"a hamstring injury\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tola added: 'I was fully prepared and knew I could fulfil my dream.\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2173, \"end\": 2177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\", \"score\": 0.9999997355239779, \"rank\": 2.6040922495005336e-07, \"text\": \"Tola\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dream\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am happy to do that.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the Olympics and it is not easy to win the Olympic Games, not at all.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very proud, very happy.'\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cairess sat in second spot after 30km before dropping back but he overtook Ethiopia's Deresa Geleta and Akira Akasaki to finish fourth.\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2448, \"end\": 2456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9999949395588176, \"rank\": 5.008754240550119e-06, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}, {\"begin\": 2477, \"end\": 2482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akira_Nogami\", \"score\": 0.9999999965125426, \"rank\": 3.487657379114436e-09, \"text\": \"Akira\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akira_Nogami\", \"dbpedia\": \"